trans-unit.source: Provides a cached dictionary that associates resource dictionaries with their URIs.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en bufret ordliste som knytter ressursen ordlister deres URIer.

trans-unit.source: Implements the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.MarkupExtensions> class that provides XAML markup extensions.
trans-unit.target: Implementerer den <xref:System.Windows.Markup.MarkupExtensions>klasse som gir XAML markup utvidelser.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.MarkupExtensions>

trans-unit.source: Markup extensions return objects based on string attribute values or markup elements in XAML.
trans-unit.target: Markup utvidelser Returner objekter som er basert på attributtet strengverdier eller markeringselementer i XAML.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.CachedResourceDictionaryExtension.ProvideValue%2A> method of each extension can use an [IServiceProvider](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) object at run time that can provide context.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.CachedResourceDictionaryExtension.ProvideValue%2A>metode for hver filtype kan bruke en [IServiceProvider](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) objektet ved kjøretid som kan gi kontekst.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.CachedResourceDictionaryExtension.ProvideValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.CachedResourceDictionaryExtension"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.CachedResourceDictionaryExtension"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns an object that is set as the value of the target property for this markup extension.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et objekt som er angitt som verdien for egenskapen target for denne markup filtypen.

trans-unit.source: The ProvideValue method of each extension can use an [IServiceProvider](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) object at run time that can provide context.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ProvideValue for hver filtype kan bruke en [IServiceProvider](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) objektet ved kjøretid som kan gi kontekst.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IServiceProvider> object that can provide services for the markup extension.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IServiceProvider>objekt som kan gi tjenester for markup filtypen.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Object> value to set on the property where the extension is applied.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Object>verdien for egenskapen der utvidelsen skal brukes.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URI associated with this cached resource dictionary extension.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir URI som er knyttet til denne bufrede ressursen ordlisten filtypen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Uri> associated with this cached resource dictionary extension.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Uri>som er forbundet med denne bufrede ressursen ordliste utvidelsen.</xref:System.Uri>
